FBIS4-6766 "dreas079_i_94005" FBIS-EAS-94-079 Daily Report 23 Apr 1994 Cambodia Sihanouk Appreciative of Leaders' Support Sihanouk Appreciative of Leaders' Support Message to Ranariddh, Hun Sen BK2304092794 Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network in Cambodian 0452 GMT 23 Apr 94 BK2304092794 Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network in Cambodian 0452 GMT 23 Apr 94 Cambodian BFN ["Message of His Majesty Norodom Sihanouk to First Prime Minister Norodom Ranariddh and Second Prime Minister Hun Sen"; dated 22 April -- read by announcer] [Text] Beloved Prince Norodom Ranariddh and Samdech Hun Sen: Today, I was deeply moved to receive the message of support from the RGC -- with both of you as first and second prime ministers -- for my 22 April 1994 statement concerning a round-table meeting for peace and national reconciliation. I would like to express my deepest and warmest thanks to you and the RGC for your constant demonstration of responsibility, which is imbued with sublime and fine patriotism. Both of you and the RGC members, please accept my warmest and deepest affectionate regards. [Signed] Norodom Sihanouk. [Dated] Phnom Penh, 22 April 1994.
